{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"fa4wnbx592ldn2ymb87u7hd","title":"HKPORI|香港民研","desc":"","updated":1653381309452,"created":1648712062179,"custom":{},"fname":"sites.pori","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"84bd0a3846549cda643f5722fab6e9f7","links":[{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"sites.pori","id":"fa4wnbx592ldn2ymb87u7hd","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"howto.replay","alias":"howto.replay","position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":143,"offset":949},"end":{"line":13,"column":176,"offset":982},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"howto.replay","anchorHeader":"reply-wacz-files"}},{"from":{"fname":"sites","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":5,"offset":228},"end":{"line":13,"column":19,"offset":242},"indent":[]},"value":"sites.pori","alias":"sites.pori"}],"anchors":{"archives":{"type":"header","text":"Archives","value":"archives","line":17,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":[],"parent":"wx39zljncctue32jn06u29u","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"hkpori香港民研\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#hkpori香港民研\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>HKPORI|香港民研</h1>\n<p>香港民意研究所（英語：Hong Kong Public Opinion Research Institute，簡稱香港民研、PORI），是一所定期進行民意調查的香港獨立民調機構，於2019年2月19日正式註冊為有限公司，同年5月4日正式營運，現任主席及行政總裁為香港大學退休助理教授鍾庭耀，副行政總裁為前香港理工大學應用社會科學系鍾劍華助理教授。該研究所前身是香港大學民意研究計劃。</p>\n<p>Hong Kong Public Opinion Research Institute (HKPORI) was officially registered as a limited company on February 19, 2019, began to operate symbolically on May 4 of the same year, and then began to operate officially and independently on July 1 of the same year. The core values of the HKPORI are science and democracy, both of which are important pillars of humanity. HKPORI stands firm on its social conscience, emulates the world’s top public opinion research institutions, and serves the public with its best knowledge and conscientiousness. --</p>\n<p>Web site: <a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/\">https://www.pori.hk/</a>\nStarted:\nEnded: </p>\n<h2 id=\"archives\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#archives\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>Archives</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"https://bafybeiae2dbmpdo5ulcll3ksx5dlqbyw2qbmuewvtqma653nlocz5gf4ay.ipfs.dweb.link/fixtures/pori-04_25_2022.wacz\">.WACZ as of 25/04/2022</a> (<a href=\"/notes/9jou94aipjmxrwmd28tly5u#reply-wacz-files\">Replay the archived files</a>)</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/*/https://www.pori.hk/\">Wayback Machine</a></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlinks</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/notes/wx39zljncctue32jn06u29u\">Collections</a></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"pfy4h1nwep9age7eg0u8xe1","title":"SHKO(Save Hong Kong Online)","desc":"","updated":1754149906369,"created":1648525691085,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"b2342439d1f39036b77dfb5a9d257bac","links":[{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"pfy4h1nwep9age7eg0u8xe1","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"sites.rfa_cantonese","alias":"RFA Cantonese","position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":125,"offset":807},"end":{"line":7,"column":162,"offset":844},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"sites.rfa_cantonese"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"pfy4h1nwep9age7eg0u8xe1","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"sites","alias":"websites or online causes","position":{"start":{"line":18,"column":34,"offset":1448},"end":{"line":18,"column":71,"offset":1485},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"sites"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"pfy4h1nwep9age7eg0u8xe1","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"howto","alias":"contribute","position":{"start":{"line":18,"column":201,"offset":1615},"end":{"line":18,"column":223,"offset":1637},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"howto"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"pfy4h1nwep9age7eg0u8xe1","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"sponsorship","alias":"sponsor","position":{"start":{"line":18,"column":246,"offset":1660},"end":{"line":18,"column":271,"offset":1685},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"sponsorship"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"pfy4h1nwep9age7eg0u8xe1","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"sites.appledaily","position":{"start":{"line":21,"column":3,"offset":1736},"end":{"line":21,"column":23,"offset":1756},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"sites.appledaily"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"pfy4h1nwep9age7eg0u8xe1","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"sites.inmediahk","position":{"start":{"line":22,"column":3,"offset":1771},"end":{"line":22,"column":22,"offset":1790},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"sites.inmediahk"}}],"anchors":{"goals":{"type":"header","text":"Goals","value":"goals","line":17,"column":0,"depth":2},"quick-facts":{"type":"header","text":"Quick Facts","value":"quick-facts","line":22,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":["fzfda8r3h330gsr6wg5db9w","dr6y9n9s72kljfnr7bpwvqj","iu6nr9qel896bjhbckfl05d","vzihkvznemcaaef2br0s1co","wx39zljncctue32jn06u29u","brr1zrug1jl02gi80d1dv8c"],"parent":null,"data":{},"body":"\n[![Great Extinction](/assets/extinctions.jpeg)](/notes/wx39zljncctue32jn06u29u/) \n> (_Courtesy: [Hong Kong Freepress](https://hongkongfp.com/2021/11/28/explainer-over-50-groups-gone-in-11-months-how-hong-kongs-pro-democracy-forces-crumbled/), 2021_) \n\nSHKO (Save Hong Kong Online) is a community-driven project dedicated to preserving the rapidly disappearing websites and online resources of Hong Kong’s civil society and independent media since 2019. In response to the sweeping shutdowns caused by political changes in Hong Kong, we aim to safeguard digital heritage before it vanishes. This project is anonymous, open source, and supported by a global network of contributors.\n\nWhile most sites in our archive were forced offline due to Hong Kong’s political deterioration, it’s important to note that [[RFA Cantonese|sites.rfa_cantonese]] is the only site here closed not because of Hong Kong’s situation, but due to internal political decisions in the United States.\n\nExplore our full list of preserved sites and archives on the [Collections page](/notes/wx39zljncctue32jn06u29u/).\n\n## Goals\n- To preserve as much information as possible before its disappearance during Hong Kong's great transition\n- To illustrate a viable method that everyone can use to help preserve online heritage with no pains\n- To demonstrate global collaborations to save local digital heritages with best practices\n\n## Quick Facts\n\nWe are working on over dozens of [[websites or online causes | sites]] in Hong Kong in the past two decades which has been forced to shutdown or at the brink of disappearing. We'd welcome anyone help [[contribute | howto]] to the content and/or [[sponsor | sponsorship]] our program to sustain it together. \n\nExamples:\n- [[sites.appledaily]] (Extincted)\n- [[sites.inmediahk]] (In Danger)\n\n\n\n"},"collectionChildren":null,"customHeadContent":null,"config":{"version":5,"dev":{"enablePreviewV2":true},"commands":{"lookup":{"note":{"selectionMode":"extract","confirmVaultOnCreate":true,"vaultSelectionModeOnCreate":"smart","leaveTrace":false,"bubbleUpCreateNew":true,"fuzzThreshold":0.2}},"randomNote":{},"insertNote":{"initialValue":"templates"},"insertNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"none","enableMultiSelect":false},"insertNoteIndex":{"enableMarker":false},"copyNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"title"},"templateHierarchy":"template"},"workspace":{"vaults":[{"fsPath":"vault"}],"journal":{"dailyDomain":"daily","name":"journal","dateFormat":"y.MM.dd","addBehavior":"childOfDomain"},"scratch":{"name":"scratch","dateFormat":"y.MM.dd.HHmmss","addBehavior":"asOwnDomain"},"task":{"name":"","dateFormat":"","addBehavior":"childOfCurrent","statusSymbols":{"":" ","wip":"w